                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1cg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      If you want the complete experience of the Andamans then I would suggest that you should book tickets for a sail from Chennai. Enjoy three days of fun in the ocean blues and you are up for a treat. If you tend to be a bit sea-sick then don’t worry a bit because you can fly to the Veer Savarkar International Airport in Port Blair."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewad2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="Best Time To Visit"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1dg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      Come summer and the Andamans just gives you that lovely tropical tinge. Though the heat can be a bit mean at times, you can cool off in the surrounding deep blue ocean. So now you know the best time to visit the Andamans. Just make sure you don’t visit the place in the raging monsoons."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewae2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="Availability Of Guides"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
